creator: Tina Karol
descriptionHtml:
"Znayty svoih" is Tina Karol's seventh studio album. The sylph as a personification of air lightness and earth force is the central element of the album. It was integrated in the AR-application, where users can interact with the sculpture and view the animation by scanning the QR-code or surface and placing it in AR.

AR-activities are being added and will be used during the concert for the immersive effect of the live show. Stay tuned.
title: Tina Karol

creator: Tina Karol
descriptionHtml:
Discover the three-dimensional performance of Tina Karol's new song in augmented reality.

Tina's performance was captured on video, creating a 3D recording of the performance. Press "Start" to place Tina in your surroundings and enjoy a virtual surprise.

Change effects, change scale, change colors - record your creative video and post it on social networks with the hashtag #тинахорошийпарень.

"Horoshiy paren" is the second single from Tina Karol's new album, which is available for pre-order now.

Sassy girl in the virtual world or gang member - that's how Tina will appear before you in augmented reality.

Listen and add the song to your playlist on all streaming platforms
Let me into your world, let us become even closer.

title: Tina Karol

creator: Tina Karol
descriptionHtml:
Discover the three-dimensional performance of Tina Karol's songs in augmented reality.

Click AR concert to see special effects during Tina's live performance. Select the song, point the camera at the stage and press start. Change scale, placement of content, record incredible videos and share them on social media.

In the application, special effects are available for two Tina's songs - "Naity Svoih" and "Horoshiy paren". Also, you can use the embedded karaoke to sing your favorite songs together with Tina.

Click the AR clip to integrate Tina into your surroundings and enjoy watching the virtual surprise. Tina's performance was captured on video, creating a 3D-recording of the performance.

Change effects, change scale, choose colors - record your creative video and post it on social networks with the hashtag #тинахорошийпарень.


"Horoshiy paren" is the second single from Tina Karol's new album. Sassy girl in the virtual world - this is how Tina will appear in front of you in this augmented reality.


Listen and add the song to your playlist on all streaming platforms
Let me into your world, let us become even closer.

Looking forward to your incredible art video!

Love, your "good guy" Tina 😂

* AR clip option is available only for devices that support ARCore and ARKit.
